## –î–∏—Ö–æ—Ç–æ–º–∏—á–Ω–æ —Ç—ä—Ä—Å–µ–Ω–µ
*binary search*

```cpp
bool binary_search(const int *arr, unsigned n, int x) {  
    int l = 0;  
    int r = n - 1;  

    while (r >= l) {  
        unsigned m = l + (r - l) / 2;  

        if (arr[m] == x) {  
            return true;  
        } else {  
            if (arr[m] < x) {  
                l = m + 1;  
            } else {  
                r = m - 1;  
            }  
        }  
    }  

    return false;  
}
```

